column5: Well....  He came alot sooner than we expected but on Saturday morning my new fishing and hunting partner arrived.  He is 8 weeks old and already a tank.  A pure bred Alaskan Malamute named Gus.  He is already showing his temperment, albeit stubborn...he is amazing.
OMG... he is so cute... and he is going to be huge!!!! I hope you have a bimini top on your boat cuz with all that fur he's going to be one hot dog under the sun!!!! gorgeous!!
awww to cute!  Looks like he will be a fine fishing partner!  Cheers!
Huge paws. He is going to be a monster!
Thanks....we are going out fishing tonight and hopefully he will be alright.
nice...  Love the paws... he ain't getting stuck in the snow, that's for sure!!
Thats one nice looking pup. Enjoy
how adorable !!!!!! they don't stay small for long my dog is taller than I am now lol
Beautiful pup!!!  I hope that isn't Malamute whiz in the floorboards of your truck in the first pic?
